+```
+Technical Specification (TS) – Crypto Portfolio & Risk Analyzer App
+1. Project Overview
+
+The Crypto Portfolio & Risk Analyzer App helps users track their cryptocurrency investments, analyze portfolio performance, assess risks, and make informed decisions. The app provides real-time price tracking, alerts, analytics, and advanced risk metrics.
+
+Goal: Allow users to manage crypto assets effectively, understand risk exposure, and optimize portfolio allocation.
+
+2. Functional Requirements
+2.1 Portfolio Management
+
+Users can add multiple wallets and exchanges.
+
+Add cryptocurrencies with:
+
+Name / Symbol
+
+Quantity
+
+Purchase price / date
+
+Notes (optional)
+
+Manual entry or API integration with major exchanges (Binance, Coinbase, Kraken, etc.).
+
+2.2 Real-Time Price Tracking
+
+Track prices of cryptocurrencies in real-time.
+
+Display portfolio value in multiple fiat currencies.
+
+Graphs showing price trends over different timeframes (1h, 24h, 7d, 30d, 1y).
+
+2.3 Risk Analysis
+
+Calculate portfolio risk metrics:
+
+Volatility
+
+Sharpe ratio
+
+Maximum drawdown
+
+Correlation between assets
+
+Simulate potential losses/gains based on market scenarios.
+
+Highlight overexposure to single assets or high-risk coins.
+
+2.4 Alerts & Notifications
+
+Price alerts for specific coins (threshold up/down).
+
+Portfolio value alerts (daily/weekly).
+
+Risk exposure warnings when thresholds are exceeded.
+
+2.5 Analytics & Reporting
+
+Dashboard showing portfolio allocation, top gainers/losers, and risk metrics.
+
+Pie charts, bar charts, and line graphs for visualization.
+
+Historical performance charts.
+
+Export portfolio report to PDF or CSV.
+
+2.6 Security & Authentication
+
+Optional two-factor authentication (2FA).
+
+Encrypted local storage for sensitive data.
+
+API keys for exchange integration stored securely.
+
+Optional biometric login (fingerprint/face).
+
+2.7 User Interface
+
+Dashboard with portfolio summary, value, and risk score.
+
+Detailed coin page with performance metrics and historical charts.
+
+Portfolio analytics page showing risk and allocation.
+
+Light/Dark mode and customizable themes.
+
+3. Non-Functional Requirements
+3.1 Platform
+
+Mobile: iOS & Android
+
+Optional Web Dashboard
+
+3.2 Performance
+
+Real-time price updates (<2 seconds delay).
+
+Smooth navigation between portfolio, analytics, and alerts.
+
+Load portfolio of 100+ assets quickly (<1 second).
+
+3.3 Data Storage
+
+Local database (SQLite, Realm, Hive) for offline data.
+
+Cloud sync optional for multi-device access with encryption.
+
+3.4 Security
+
+End-to-end encryption for API keys and sensitive data.
+
+Optional multi-factor authentication.
+
+3.5 Usability
+
+Intuitive UI for both beginner and advanced crypto users.
+
+Easy portfolio addition/editing and alert setup.
+
+Responsive design for mobile and web.
+
+4. Technical Stack
+Mobile
+
+Framework: Flutter or React Native
+
+Local DB: SQLite, Realm, or Hive
+
+APIs: CoinGecko, CoinMarketCap, or exchange-specific APIs
+
+Notifications: native push/local
+
+Web (Optional)
+
+Frontend: React / Vue.js
+
+Backend: Node.js / Django
+
+Database: PostgreSQL / MongoDB
+
+5. Future Enhancements
+
+AI-powered portfolio optimization (rebalancing suggestions).
+
+Predictive analytics for potential price movements.
+
+Integration with DeFi protocols and staking dashboards.
+
+Social trading features: see top portfolios or strategies (optional).
+
+Advanced charting with interactive indicators (MACD, RSI, Bollinger Bands).
+```
+
